1. sudo apt update
2. sudo apt install tasksel
3. sudo tasksel 
   -> new window open then select ->KDE Plasma (space key use to select and up down arrow to move, Tab key use to ok) its install time may be 15/30 then
4. ip a (here you show ip address but you choose second 2 no ip like its start 172.... )
5. windows search panel -> then search Remote Desktop Connection -> then pase ip address -> use ubuntu user name and password
